{"tid":1679301,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"舊 iPhone 保值不再？iPhone XR 大舖跌到三字頭","createTime":"2019-10-28T06:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T11:28:40.000Z","uid":109923,"like":92,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"5d65e6b595571afaf23e84785bcfc2f18e24a729","tid":1679301,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:42:03.000Z","msg":"老老實實，版主係前 iPhone XR 用家，最近先終於升咗上 iPhone 11 Pro。用咗 iPhone XR 一段時間，講缺點佢真係唔多，舊電算係夠長氣，最主要係得一個鏡頭，連超廣角呢啲功能都用唔到，先至令我想換機。一部咁好嘅手機，但估唔到罕見咁不停跌價，近呢幾個星期，幾乎個個星期都有減價，今個星期已經大舖價跌到三字頭，呢個價絕對合理！睇下文啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YL1jhQg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYL1jhQg.png&h=c689ac8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又係豐澤，可能 iPhone XR 存貨太多，所以 Apple 都借助豐澤，為呢堆手機清貨。不過今次跌到三字頭嘅 iPhone XR，只限一種顏色，就係珊瑚色，最新清貨價為 $3900；至於紅色同黃色，就維持 $4420；最貴依然係白色同藍色，賣價 $4845，呢個價相信暫時未跌穿網友心理關口。但 $3900 買到珊瑚色 iPhone XR，基本上都唔使再介意佢係乜顏色，反正買咗返嚟之後，最後都係會笠返個套，咁先夠安全。心動嗎？"},{"pid":"230fc9d16bdba3c16df2916aab2fa4d2a80eff92","tid":1679301,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:42:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Mfv693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Mfv693.jpg&h=975a7fc9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ce0fbe5ba79d8f2b8a6964c54ae1f11a498d773b","tid":1679301,"uid":128489,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T06:43:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"efc0848d624926f3540a4e892e9d214f82fbb171","tid":1679301,"uid":80481,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T07:26:12.000Z","msg":"XS max跌得仲勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過豐澤個價睇下就算，撳極都買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<im